# Dataset Description
## Overview
This folder contains input data used for power system flexibility analysis.

## Files

### 5_years_GBN_dataset.csv

### input_data.csv
- Hourly load demand (MW)
- Renewable generation profiles (wind, solar)

### generator_data.csv
- Capacity (MW)
- Ramp rates
- Operational constraints

## Source
- Synthetic data based on typical power system scenarios
- Inspired by real-world operational characteristics

## Notes
All values are normalized and used for simulation purposes.

